          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We want you to receive your <strong>Anymaka</strong> products quickly and reliably — no matter where you are. Below you’ll find shipping details tailored to each of our supported markets: the <strong>United States</strong>, <strong>United Kingdom</strong>, <strong>Canada</strong>, and <strong>Australia</strong>.</p><p></p><p>*<strong>Please allow 1 to 3 business days for us to dispatch your order</strong> (please note: shipping times may vary due to uncontrollable factors such as political events, changes in climate, and so forth). We do not process orders or shipping on weekends or holidays.</p><p></p>",
