            "text": "<p>We will not be shipping or delivering on national holiday, including:</p><ul><li>New Year’s Day</li><li>Easter Sunday</li><li>Memorial Day / Bank Holidays</li><li>Independence Day (US) / Canada Day / Australia Day</li><li>Labor Day</li><li>Thanksgiving Day (US)</li><li>Christmas Eve</li><li>Christmas Day</li></ul><p>Please note that shipping estimates start the next business day after holidays.</p>",
